--- !u!114 &640470350
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 640470348}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f4688fdb7df04437aeb418b961361dc5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "The Floorian Man was invited to a birthday party on the day of his sudden
    passing. His initial goal was to bake a nice cake, which would fit for the celebration.
    However, he already had trouble preparing the first ingredient as his piece of
    butter was frozen solid and therefore impossible to be cut with a regular knife.
    On top of that, he didn't even have a proper knife since his only one got stuck
    in a foolish attempt to open a can of raviolis. In a desperate manner, he used
    his circular saw in the basement to cut the butter. Unfortunately, he cut his
    finger off in the process. Suffering this severe injury, he rushed into his bedroom
    to put on some music for comfort as instructed on his emergency note. Since that
    couldn't possibly put him at ease, he went into his living room to call 811.
    Little did he know there was still a leftover banana peel lying on the ground
    from a banana he had previously been eaten. He tripped on the peel and fell to
    the floor while accidentally turning his ceiling fan to full speed. The fan's
    engine broke due to mechanical exhaustion and rotated with tremendous speed.
    The shurikens attached to the fan's rotor blades quickly gained momentum and
    snapped from the strings. They then flew with full force into the Floorian Man's
    back, killing him instantly. The Floorian Man was never murdered but instead
    died because of his own failure. \r\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: efa4ffbb82bf63347a6f4012102bfa50, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 7747139189407029343, guid: efa4ffbb82bf63347a6f4012102bfa50, type: 2}
